{"id": 834, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪些人自以为懂你？", "description": "哇你看这件衣服真的好“你”哦！！拿过来一看吐血三升。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 2830, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183641JM5Hxz3GBpZ9OLIw.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-25T11:07:21Z", "options": [{"id": 53762, "content": "理发师", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488506}, {"id": 58114, "content": "这不是关心你吗?！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504131}, {"id": 54531, "content": "我爸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458051}, {"id": 53764, "content": "鸡排切开就不好吃了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488506}, {"id": 53766, "content": "对对，是的是的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490474}, {"id": 61959, "content": "你应该怎么怎么样……关你屁事？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536541}, {"id": 53768, "content": "“我是最了解你的”", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468649}, {"id": 53769, "content": "你和我前女友很像", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490490}, {"id": 53770, "content": "数学老师：这一题这么简单你们都不会？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464177}, {"id": 53771, "content": "这个不放糖会很酸哦！你是不是在减肥？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490490}, {"id": 53772, "content": "你这么努力 是学霸吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360185}, {"id": 53773, "content": "多喝热水", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 472086}, {"id": 53775, "content": "我跟你说！你就是太天真！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450615}, {"id": 53776, "content": "你选的发型不如我给你设计这款~能够遮住你的脸型", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450615}, {"id": 53777, "content": "啊~好爽啊~你也到高潮了吧？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450615}, {"id": 53778, "content": "“给你新买了衣服哦”“你不是喜欢吃这个吗”讲真，衣服很丑，所谓的喜欢吃也只不过是不厌恶的偶尔会吃..", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 210449}, {"id": 56085, "content": "哎呀你不就那点小事儿嘛  我小时候都经历过的  没什么~", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504677}, {"id": 53783, "content": "给你介绍个土豪(不管三七二十一)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473610}, {"id": 53784, "content": "等你长大就懂了????", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482446}, {"id": 53785, "content": "长大你就知道啦??", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482446}, {"id": 53786, "content": "你怎么胖成这样了？！不能再胖了！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490560}, {"id": 54303, "content": "这个男的不错就这个了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494993}, {"id": 53793, "content": "我在你这么大的时候……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171786}, {"id": 53794, "content": "我看你呀，都不会这样做啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201081}, {"id": 53796, "content": "妈觉得冷", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473350}, {"id": 53798, "content": "我觉得你应该和我想的差不多。 我知道你喜欢玫瑰花！（抱歉，本女子不喜欢）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490676}, {"id": 53799, "content": "做人要圆滑点。", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004852sMaIk6wKBZ13dTpR.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 121608}, {"id": 53800, "content": "你不这样就不是你了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490702}, {"id": 53802, "content": "残忍拒绝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212}, {"id": 53803, "content": "我觉得你现在这样就挺好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 247838}, {"id": 53804, "content": "你这样那样，肯定是在装 B.", "image": "img/option/option/20160606144921KOmVudj18G4nMSCh.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 483371}, {"id": 53805, "content": "你是江西人，肯定能吃辣。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490766}, {"id": 53806, "content": "情商不高的男票", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449851}, {"id": 53808, "content": "我最会看人，我看上的人！不会错！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488790}, {"id": 53810, "content": "看到一句话“钱可以再赚，衣服下架了就没了”，幡然醒悟！突然好想冲去商店买上上次还有上次嫌贵没买的那件zara风衣。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490788}, {"id": 54326, "content": "一边玩去，小爷又不是穿给你看的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 282152}, {"id": 57143, "content": "我都是过来人 我都懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511413}, {"id": 57399, "content": "这件事你肯定同意", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 512530}, {"id": 53560, "content": "你的头发有点油我给你用我们这个刚到的新款去油洗发水吧？??", "image": null, "praise_count": 88, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 414097}, {"id": 53561, "content": "先生游泳健身吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177319}, {"id": 53564, "content": "这个一个穿上挺洋气的\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 359971}, {"id": 54332, "content": "要求不要那么高...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495183}, {"id": 54077, "content": "恩，我知道你是一个外表女王，内心其实很脆弱很需要陪伴和依靠的女生。滚蛋好么，毕竟我不是按理出牌的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493011}, {"id": 54333, "content": "是时候该...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495183}, {"id": 53566, "content": "这男的不错给你介绍介绍？", "image": null, "praise_count": 224, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459807}, {"id": 53567, "content": "理发师：这个发型颜色很适合你啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 147, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 489170}, {"id": 53568, "content": "我这是为你好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 614, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 59712, "content": "有的人，自己为有点小智商，就伴高富帅……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 523033}, {"id": 53569, "content": "女士，您可以试试我们新到的祛痘产品？！很好用！", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 452995}, {"id": 62019, "content": "老妈：把秋裤穿上", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536887}]}